OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBritish Gas to carry out   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmeter fitting in-house     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, British Gas has said it will carry out 
OL,6, any future force-fitting of prepayment 
OL,7, meters itself following an outcry over 
OL,8, how a contractor had behaved.          
OL,10,FA report by the Times found agents     
OL,11,Facting for British Gas had forced their
OL,12,Fway into vulnerable people's homes.    
OL,14,FA review found there had been "no      
OL,15,Fsystemic issues" with prepayment meters
OL,16,F(PPMs) fitted under warrant.           
OL,18,FHowever, it added that in a small      
OL,19,Fnumber of cases, "things have gone     
OL,20,Fwrong".                                
